➜【星连文学社】广东诗人小隐：立秋三首
http://www.sohu.com/a/412026865_100115135	49860
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>今日，时逢立秋，聚会不成有感：万事只求半称心</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>立秋三首</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（文/小隐）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200807/d0c34306b00f42308792ec570c11f45b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>其一</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋日艳骄阳，初心且隐堂。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三秋无聚会，归去拭浓妆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200807/8ae2ae026ab44370a849902a4c5b0c4f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>其二</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">落幕斜阳绿渐匀，西窗风景入红尘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今年戏说闲年事，万里江河日日新。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200807/b63cf39a1f4d4452b3782744f8bb5bf1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
